data.description: Beautiful 4 Bedroom Home in Lansing, IL    This attractive brick/vinyl two-story home is in one of Lansing's newer subdivisions. It features four bedrooms, three bathrooms, and approximately 2800 square feet of finished living space.    The main level has a living room, formal dining room, guest bathroom, and updated kitchen with new stainless steel appliances and faucet. The kitchen is open to the family room with a gas fireplace.    The upper level has a main bathroom and four spacious bedrooms, including a master bedroom with a private bathroom.    The basement is mostly finished and features a rec room, storage space, a basement bar, and roughed-in plumbing for a 4th bathroom.    The home also has a 2.5-car attached garage, a covered front porch, and a nice deck in the fenced backyard. No homes are directly behind the home, as it backs up to a greenbelt/water retention area.    Features:    Four bedrooms  Three bathrooms  Approximately 2800 square feet of finished living space  Updated kitchen with new stainless steel appliances and faucet  Gas fireplace in the family room  Mostly finished basement with rec room, storage space, basement bar, and roughed-in plumbing for a 4th bathroom  2.5 car attached garage  Covered front porch  Nice deck in the fenced backyard  Located in one of Lansing's newer subdivisions  Benefits:    Move-in ready, but needs a little TLC  Plenty of space   Great for entertaining  Convenient location in a newer subdivision  No homes directly behind the home  Schedule your showing today to see this beautiful home for yourself!
